precis:
Regulations Amending the TOBACCO REGULATIONS by, inter alia, prescribing
the marking requirement for export that do not exceed the 1.5% export limit
set in the Act and by eliminating the marking requirement for imported
tobacco products destined for Canadian duty free shops.
